{"segment_id": "shijing__song-shangsong-003__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "song-shangsong-003", "source_id": "song-shangsong-003__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·頌·商頌·003.1", "text_original": "天命玄鳥，降而生商，宅殷土芒芒。古帝命武湯，正域彼四方。", "text_normalized": "天命玄鳥，降而生商，宅殷土芒芒。古帝命武湯，正域彼四方。", "notes": "玄鳥 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__song-shangsong-003__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "song-shangsong-003", "source_id": "song-shangsong-003__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·頌·商頌·003.2", "text_original": "方命厥后，奄有九有。商之先后，受命不殆，在武丁孫子。", "text_normalized": "方命厥后，奄有九有。商之先后，受命不殆，在武丁孫子。", "notes": "玄鳥 Chinese stanza 2."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__song-shangsong-003__003__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "song-shangsong-003", "source_id": "song-shangsong-003__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "詩經·頌·商頌·003.3", "text_original": "武丁孫子，武王靡不勝。龍旂十乘，大糦是承。", "text_normalized": "武丁孫子，武王靡不勝。龍旂十乘，大糦是承。", "notes": "玄鳥 Chinese stanza 3."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__song-shangsong-003__004__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "song-shangsong-003", "source_id": "song-shangsong-003__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 4, "canonical_ref": "詩經·頌·商頌·003.4", "text_original": "邦畿千里，維民所止，肇域彼四海。四海來假，來假祁祁。", "text_normalized": "邦畿千里，維民所止，肇域彼四海。四海來假，來假祁祁。", "notes": "玄鳥 Chinese stanza 4."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__song-shangsong-003__005__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "song-shangsong-003", "source_id": "song-shangsong-003__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 5, "canonical_ref": "詩經·頌·商頌·003.5", "text_original": "景員維河，殷受命咸宜，百祿是何。", "text_normalized": "景員維河，殷受命咸宜，百祿是何。", "notes": "玄鳥 Chinese stanza 5."}
